description: TEHRAN – Iran’s top security official announced on Wednesday that Tehran supports any peace plan like the one proposed by China and Brazil that would be acceptable by both Russia and Ukraine, IRNA reported.
title: Iran backs China-Brazil peace plan for Ukraine war

description: The Palestinian Civil Defence has said that at least 14 people, including women and children, were killed in an Israeli air attack on a school-turned-shelter in the Nuseirat school in central Gaza Strip.
title: Women, children are torn into pieces in attack on Gaza school

description: TEHRAN – Russian Foreign Minister Sergei Lavrov has invited new Iranian Foreign Minister Abbas Araghchi to visit Moscow, Russian Foreign Ministry spokeswoman Maria Zakharova announced on Wednesday.
title: Lavrov invites Iranian FM to Russia

description: Egyptian President Abdel Fattah El Sisi on Wednesday denounced the use of “hunger as a weapon” in the Gaza war, describing the Israeli tactic as “very, very grave”.
title: Egypt's El Sisi: Israel using hunger as a weapon in Gaza

description: TEHRAN – Iran’s Foreign Minister Abbas Araqhchi on Wednesday insisted on Tehran’s previous announcements that the Islamic Republic has not sent ballistic missiles to Russia, saying the United States and the European trio of Britain, France and Germany are again acting on “faulty intelligence”.
title: US, E3 acting on faulty intelligence, Iran says of claims of missile sale to Russia

description: TEHRAN - President Masoud Pezeshkian on Wednesday emphasized the need for full implementation of security cooperation agreements between Iran and neighboring Iraq.
title: Pezeshkian urges implementation of security agreements with Iraq

description: TEHRAN – Iraq and Iraq signed 14 cooperation documents in commercial, economic, cultural, and social areas on Wednesday.
title: Iran, Iraq ink 14 cooperation documents

description: TEHRAN – In a common position on Wednesday, Iranian President Masoud Pezeshkian and Iraqi Prime Minister Mohammed Shia' Al-Sudani said it is the responsibility of the international community to put an end to the Israeli “crimes” and “genocide” against the Palestinian people in the Gaza Strip, the office of the Iraqi prime minister said in a statement.
title: Iran's Pezeshkian, Iraq's Sudani demand end to Israeli genocide in Gaza

description: It might catch your attention that Farsi Language surprisingly growing and more and more are interested in Learning Farsi and understanding literature, especially poems in Persian.
title: Best Way to Learn Farsi Quickly & Easily

description: The BRICS Literary Forum will be held in Kazan on Wednesday, 11 September. Famous writers, poets and translators from Brazil, India, China, the United Arab Emirates (UAE) and Iran will come to the capital of Tatarstan and exchange experience in their activities.
title: BRICS literary masters to meet in Kazan to exchange experience
